snippet.title: Lo-Fi for Monsters (and eldritch horrors) [lofi/ calm/ chill beats to steal souls to]
snippet.description:
Link to the free game "A Monster's Insight": https://arkicade.itch.io/a-monsters-insight

Link to full OST: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V743telSEIA&ab_channel=LGMgoblinmusic

"A Monster's Insight" is a cosmic horror-themed "debating" visual novel with psychological elements. This game is all about the power of words and how you can exploit them.

Link to arkicade's (game dev/artist) page: https://arkicade.itch.io/

Link to LGM's (music composer's) page: https://lgmsoundsgoodman.itch.io/
